(2, U&'2023-c\00fc il aprelin 1-d\0259 f\00fcsunkar gec\0259d\0259 tan\0131nm\0131\015f t\00fcrk m\00fc\011f\0259nnisi Serdar Orta\00e7 Bak\0131 Konqres M\0259rk\0259zind\0259 s\0259hn\0259y\0259 \00e7\0131xark\0259n Bak\0131dak\0131 musiqisev\0259rl\0259r unudulmaz t\0259\0259ss\00fcrat ya\015fad\0131lar. Ehtirasla rezonans do\011furan s\0259si v\0259 ruha toxunan s\00f6zl\0259ri il\0259 Orta\00e7\0131n konserti s\0259n\0259tkarl\0131q, istedad v\0259 musiqinin birl\0259\015fdirici g\00fcc\00fcn\00fcn t\0259nt\0259n\0259si idi. G\0259lin bu \0259lam\0259tdar hadis\0259nin sehrli atmosferini ara\015fd\0131raq. \00d6z m\00f6ht\0259\015f\0259mliyi v\0259 akustikas\0131 il\0259 tan\0131nan Bak\0131 Konqres M\0259rk\0259zi Serdar Orta\00e7\0131n musiqi ekstravaqanzas\0131 \00fc\00e7\00fcn m\00fck\0259mm\0259l fon yaratm\0131\015fd\0131r. M\0259kan h\0259v\0259sli p\0259r\0259sti\015fkarlar\0131 il\0259 dolduqca, intizar havada as\0131ld\0131 v\0259 qeyri-adi \0259yl\0259nc\0259 gec\0259si v\0259d ed\0259n elektrik atmosferi yaratd\0131. \018fn\0259n\0259vi t\00fcrk melodiyalar\0131n\0131 m\00fcasir ritml\0259rl\0259 harmanlayan maestro Serdar Orta\00e7 ilk notdan tama\015fa\00e7\0131lar\0131 valeh etdi. Onun z\0259ngin, emosional s\0259si auditoriyada \0259ks-s\0259da verir, dinl\0259yicil\0259ri dil v\0259 m\0259d\0259niyy\0259t s\0259rh\0259dl\0259rini a\015fan musiqi s\0259yah\0259tin\0259 c\0259lb edirdi. \0130stedadl\0131 bir qrupun m\00fc\015fayi\0259ti il\0259 Orta\00e7, bir s\0259n\0259t\00e7i kimi \00e7ox y\00f6nl\00fc oldu\011funu n\00fcmayi\015f etdirdi. Orta\00e7\0131n \0259n g\00fccl\00fc t\0259r\0259fl\0259rind\0259n biri onun tama\015fa\00e7\0131lar\0131 il\0259 d\0259rin emosional \0259laq\0259 yaratmaq bacar\0131\011f\0131ndad\0131r. \00dcr\0259kd\0259n g\0259l\0259n s\00f6zl\0259ri v\0259 k\00f6n\00fcl ox\015fayan melodiyalar\0131 il\0259 o, sevgi v\0259 sevincd\0259n tutmu\015f, h\0259sr\0259t\0259 q\0259d\0259r m\00fcxt\0259lif duy\011fular\0131 \00e