(6, U&'In the heart of Baku, Azerbaijan, music enthusiasts and partygoers experienced a night to remember on March 26, 2022, as the renowned DJ Korolova graced the stage at Ramada by Wyndham. The pulsating beats, electrifying atmosphere, and euphoric energy marked a night of sheer musical brilliance that left the audience in awe. The Ramada by Wyndham, renowned for its luxurious ambiance and exquisite event spaces, provided the perfect backdrop for this electrifying musical extravaganza. The venue buzzed with anticipation as fans, locals, and tourists gathered to witness one of the most celebrated DJs of the era.\000d\000aWith a reputation that precedes her, DJ Korolova took the stage with an aura of confidence, immediately captivating the audience with her eclectic mix of tracks spanning various genres. From pulsating techno beats to soul-stirring melodies, she masterfully curated a playlist that resonated with every individual present, ensuring there was something for everyone. One of the most remarkable aspects of the evening was the diverse audience that DJ Korolova attracted. People from different walks of life, cultures, and backgrounds converged at Ramada by Wyndham, connected by their shared love for music. The dance floor became a melting pot of energy, where strangers became friends, and barriers were broken through the universal language of music.', TIMESTAMP '0000-12-29 23:19:24', NULL, 'https://emkistorage.blob.core.windows.net/web/374740470_18291827344132244_2475564944783895848_n20231026120031087.jpg', '374740470_18291827344132244_2475564944783895848_n20231026115854571.jpg', 6, TIMESTAMP '2023-10-26 11:58:54.617016', NULL, NULL, 'Unforgettable Night of Beats and Rhythms: DJ Korolova Takes Baku by Storm at Ramada by Wyndham Concert.', 2),
