, 2023, was more than just a musical event; it was a celebration of talent, passion, and the unifying power of music. Through his extraordinary voice and heartfelt performance, Ortach created an unforgettable experience for everyone in attendance. The concert served as a reminder of the profound impact music can have, transcending barriers and bringing people together in harmony. As the night came to a close, the audience left the venue with hearts full of joy and souls touched by the magic of Serdar Ortach''s music, eager for the next opportunity to be enthralled by his artistry once again.', TIMESTAMP '0000-12-29 23:19:24', NULL, 'https://emkistorage.blob.core.windows.net/web/channels4_profile20231026120211625.jpg', 'channels4_profile20231026120221469.jpg', 6, TIMESTAMP '2023-10-26 12:02:21.491302', NULL, 22, 'A Night of Musical Brilliance: Serdar Ortach''s Unforgettable Concert at Baku Congress Center', 2);            
